Amb_Phrase: ['What I can offer is an honest explanation about what is done and why it is done.']
['SD Maid has grown so much in both user numbers and features that I need a few tools to help me keep an overview.']
["Google already provides some crash tracking via Google Play, but it's not very comfortable to use and fairly unreliable in terms of what crashs you are told about."]
['This is voluntary and you can opt out of this in the settings.\t\t\t\t']
["While I do get some numbers from Google Play, not everyone has access to Google Play and others don't want to use it."]
["It also allows me to track inofficial device features, e.g. how many devices are rooted, which Google Play doesn't track, but is a fairly important stat for SD Maid.\t\t\t\t"]
['I talk with many users via mails, read many reviews and often even watch discussion about SD Maid on social media or forums, but this is only a small glimpse.']
['What the are the most and least used features?']
['This is also voluntary and you can opt out of this in the settings.\t\t\t']
['There are quite a few people who use SD Maid without Google Play and this allows them know about updates without manually checking.\t\t\t']
